#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.97, sc211.1
msgctxt "an2.180-229:211.1.1"
msgid "“Dvīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge. "
